messages.message: When I logout and come back, I don’t see a sign in link. Only sign up? It still works to sign in that way, but it adds some confusion for returning users.

@Aayush i see that you fixed this in the landing page

should we also fix the “Sign up” label in the project nav footer? https://github.com/instabase/instabase/blob/aihub_23_04/webserver/shared/src/js/webpacked/apps/src/ai-hub/components/ProjectNav/ProjectNavFooter.tsx#L34

Sure, let me add a comment to the Figma component (https://www.figma.com/file/92YG4OQg2thnBQnFNVoQQf/AI-Hub-User-Journeys?type=design&node-id=3002-257135&t=LzTXdTouhkmaR8zL-4) for the design team to look into. The current designs do not have a sign in option in project navbar.
